OL,5, First Minister Humza Yousaf has said he
OL,6, was "disturbed" by reports of a        
OL,7, hospital board spying on bereaved      
OL,8, families.                              
OL,10,FNHS Greater Glasgow and Clyde (NHSGGC) 
OL,11,Flast week admitted paying a private    
OL,12,Fcompany to monitor the online presence 
OL,13,Fof some individuals.                   
OL,15,FOne of those named on the list, was    
OL,16,Fwidow Louise Slorance, whose husband   
OL,17,Fdied in an NHSGGC hospital.            
OL,19,FThe health board said it had apologised
OL,20,Fand had now "ceased" online monitoring.
